00:23:16.700 --> 00:23:19.950
OK, so you can have--

00:23:19.950 --> 00:23:22.190
so let me just
write a little bit.

00:23:22.190 --> 00:23:24.800
The first thing we talked about
that made the cameras move.

00:23:24.800 --> 00:23:27.800
The first thing we talked
