00:23:36.330 --> 00:23:39.750
There's just a whole lot that
comes under that heading.

00:23:39.750 --> 00:23:43.360
If you think about applying
it to air pollution,

00:23:43.360 --> 00:23:46.410
so there's a coal-fired power
plant in Salem, Massachusetts.

00:23:46.410 --> 00:23:49.770
The coal-fired power plant in
Salem, Massachusetts is dirty.

00:23:49.770 --> 00:23:52.440
Everybody in Salem
and around Salem

00:23:52.440 --> 00:23:55.910
gets affected, to some extent.

00:23:55.910 --> 00:23:57.450
How does this work?

00:23:57.450 --> 00:24:00.610
I give every person
property rights?

00:24:00.610 --> 00:24:07.680
And how do 20,000, 30,000
people act collectively?

00:24:07.680 --> 00:24:09.540
Sue in court.

00:24:09.540 --> 00:24:11.910
So when you have more than
these simple examples,

00:24:11.910 --> 00:24:17.510
it gets to be hard.

00:24:17.510 --> 00:24:21.980
And the other one,
just to fill it out,

00:24:21.980 --> 00:24:23.525
is just transaction costs.

00:24:31.080 --> 00:24:37.620
In a world in which everybody
is suing everybody else one way

00:24:37.620 --> 00:24:41.190
or another and bargaining
