parties to that convention.

01:14:21.800 --> 01:14:26.000
The third meeting produced
the Kyoto Protocol,

01:14:26.000 --> 01:14:28.940
which obliged rich countries--
those rich countries that

01:14:28.940 --> 01:14:32.540
